            <article>
                <header>
                    <h2>The Modern Gadgets</h2>
                    <div class="meta">
                        Posted By<strong> Arpit Sharma</strong><span>(2 comments)</span>
                    </div><!--meta-->
                </header>
                <img src="img/post 2.jpg" alt="Post 1">
                <p>Today the world is passing through the revolution of science and technology . The science and technology has gifted unlimited boons to humans . As a result , the humans are concentrated and are confined to these scientific instruments and gadgets .
</p><p>Parents of this new generation are working ones and find very febble time for family and children , And the children are very ill-effected due to this menace . Parents give their children smart gadgets without even thinking of the other face of the coin .
</p><p> According to the latest report from World Health Organisation , 34% of children possessing electronic devices before the age of 16 , are found to be less attentive and the level of their IQ has been reported low in comparison to others .
</p><p>Parents need to put an effort and had to make a step towards the better growth of their children as the relation between parents and children is very gentle . The bond between parents and children can work wonders for the child’s growth in every sphere .</p>
